reviewText:
I can watch all of this tapes over and over
again. All of this to me is so awesome
that I want others opinion. I give all this tapes 5 and if can more stars

I could give this drama a higher rating because the drama itself is very good. However, the English subtitling is terrible and is maybe at the best half correct. Try to buy one that comes from Korea and not Malaysia or China as I have found that the English translations are much more accurate on the ones done in Korea.
